title: The Fantastic Four - The Movie (1994)  Widescreen
description:
1994
90 minutes


In this Marvel Comic adaption, four astronauts get bombarded with cosmic rays when an accident occurs. The four of them acquire special powers, and decide to form a superhero group called the Fantastic Four.



Director: Oley Sassone


Writers: Craig J. Nevius (screenplay), Kevin Rock (screenplay)

Stars: Alex Hyde-White, Jay Underwood, Rebecca Staab
